data.description: Welcome to this beautiful brick Ranch and a Half home located on a serene 5.52-acre lot. With 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this well-maintained home is perfect for those seeking both space and comfort. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a stunning two-story great room featuring a magnificent masonry fireplace that adds warmth and character to the space. Large windows flood the area with natural light, creating a welcoming and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the great room to the adjacent kitchen and dining area, making it ideal for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen offers bay windows with built in seating with storage and a custom fitted table. The primary suite, conveniently located on the main level, offers a peaceful retreat with its generously sized bedroom and private bathroom. Upstairs, you will find two additional bedrooms, with a Jack N Jill bathroom, providing ample space and privacy. An additional Bonus Room upstairs can be used for a 4th bedroom. This home also boasts a finished basement, complete with a bar for entertaining, an office/craft room, and a theatre room - perfect for hosting movie nights or enjoying hobbies. Additionally, the new dual system Trane HVAC ensures optimal comfort throughout the year. Outside, enjoy the vast expanse of this expansive lot, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and those seeking room to roam. With two outbuildings featuring a total of seven parking bays, there is ample room for storage and hobbies. There is a space for everyone to escape, including a She-Shed! All kitchen and bar appliances are included with the sale. See attached for full list of updates. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and tranquility that this property has to offer.
